{
  "stem": "10835.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But since we didn't have any further information, we really didn't know what went on after that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And in 19-- in the beginning of 1943-- of course, we didn't know anything that was going on in the world, because at the factory, we were being watched by not SS people, profess-- who were Germans, but they were recruited from the Volksdeutsche population.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This part of Czechoslovakia was also-- they called Sudetendeutsch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there was a lot of German people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of these people were recruited into the SS to become our guards.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were guarding us at the factory and at the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some of these people we knew, because previously, we worked with them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- but then we were finding-- we were finding out little things, because the-- the head-- how should I say-- of the department, who was German, he lost two sons on the Russian front.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, he wasn't too happy about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So sometimes he would go around and cry.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he wasn't too bad of a person, so he told us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were kind of happy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every time we heard bad news happening to the Germans, we were very happy about it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Let's stop right there and we'll change tapes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
